---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="SPC 地板香港｜防水耐磨石塑地板安裝與報價｜Jupiter’s Design Limited"
  description="SPC 石塑地板適合香港住宅與舊樓翻新：防水、耐磨、安裝快捷。全港十八區上門施工，提供初步面積報價與免費現場評估。"
  lang="zh-HK"
  canonicalPath="/spc-flooring-hong-kong/"
>
  <Header lang="zh-HK" />

  <main id="top">
    <section class="editorial-hero editorial-hero--short">
      <div class="editorial-hero__image editorial-hero__image--spc" aria-hidden="true"></div>
      <div class="editorial-hero__veil" aria-hidden="true"></div>

      <div class="editorial-hero__content editorial-shell">
        <p class="editorial-kicker">SPC 石塑地板 · 香港</p>
        <h1 class="editorial-hero__title">SPC 地板，<br />為香港住宅而設的安靜基礎。</h1>
        <p class="editorial-hero__lede">
          防水、耐磨、安裝快捷。無論係居屋、私樓定係舊樓翻新，SPC 石塑地板都用一種克制而耐用嘅方式，回應香港空間嘅實際需要。
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="editorial-material">
      <div class="editorial-shell">
        <p class="editorial-kicker">為什麼選 SPC</p>
        <h2 class="editorial-material__title">適合香港的幾個理由</h2>

        <div class="editorial-material__grid">
          <article class="editorial-material__item">
            <span class="editorial-material__index">01</span>
            <h3>防水防潮</h3>
            <p>
              SPC 核心為石粉與樹脂壓製，唔怕廚房、廁所門口或回南天嘅濕氣，比實木地板更適合香港氣候。
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="editorial-material__item">
            <span class="editorial-material__index">02</span>
            <h3>耐磨抗刮</h3>
            <p>
              表面為高密度耐磨層，應付日常走動、傢俬移動同寵物爪痕都從容，長期保持平整外觀。
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="editorial-material__item">
            <span class="editorial-material__index">03</span>
            <h3>安裝快捷</h3>
            <p>
              鎖扣式卡扣，免膠免釘，多數單位一兩日內完成。適合自住翻新或出租前嘅快速換地。
            </p>
          </article>

          <article class="editorial-material__item">
            <span class="editorial-material__index">04</span>
            <h3>薄而不犧牲</h3>
            <p>
              厚度約 4–6mm，唔明顯抬高門檻同地腳線，舊樓換地時減少收口麻煩。
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="editorial-material editorial-material--alt">
      <div class="editorial-shell">
        <p class="editorial-kicker">常見問題</p>
        <h2 class="editorial-material__title">關於 SPC 地板報價與施工</h2>

        <div class="editorial-faq">
          <details class="editorial-faq__item">
            <summary>SPC 地板香港大概幾錢一呎？</summary>
            <p>
              視材料等級與施工範圍而定。你可以喺<a href="/estimate/">初步地板估算</a>輸入面積，即時查看 SPC 地板嘅預算範圍；最終報價會按現場基層、收口、拆除同搬運確認。
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="editorial-faq__item">
            <summary>舊樓翻新點處理原有地板？</summary>
            <p>
              如原有地磚或木地板狀態平穩，多數可原位鋪設 SPC；如需拆除，我哋會喺報價中列出拆舊費用，並安排清走。
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="editorial-faq__item">
            <summary>全港邊度可以上門施工？</summary>
            <p>
              服務涵蓋全港十八區，包括香港島、九龍、新界同大嶼山。我哋會先安排上門評估，再畀你確實嘅施工安排。
            </p>
          </details>

          <details class="editorial-faq__item">
            <summary>幾時可以開始？</summary>
            <p>
              確認方案同報價後，一般可於短期內排程施工。透過 WhatsApp 畀我哋相片同面積，可以先做初步估計。
            </p>
          </details>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="editorial-material">
      <div class="editorial-shell">
        <p class="editorial-kicker">施工節奏</p>
        <h2 class="editorial-material__title">從對話到完成</h2>

        <ol class="editorial-steps">
          <li><span>01</span><div><h3>對話</h3><p>由你的空間、相片與初步想法開始。</p></div></li>
          <li><span>02</span><div><h3>理解</h3><p>走進現場，看見基層、光線與使用方式。</p></div></li>
          <li><span>03</span><div><h3>選擇</h3><p>在材質、比例與耐用之間，找到合適的答案。</p></div></li>
          <li><span>04</span><div><h3>完成</h3><p>以細緻收口，讓地面成為空間的一部分。</p></div></li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="editorial-cta">
      <div class="editorial-shell">
        <p class="editorial-kicker">下一步</p>
        <h2 class="editorial-cta__title">想知你個單位嘅 SPC 地板報價？</h2>
        <p class="editorial-cta__body">
          輸入面積，即時查看預算範圍；或者經 WhatsApp 畀我哋相片，先來一次初步評估。
        </p>
        <div class="editorial-cta__actions">
          <a class="editorial-cta__primary" href="/estimate/">初步地板估算</a>
          <a class="editorial-cta__ghost" href="https://wa.me/85295715155" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">WhatsApp 查詢</a>
        </div>
        <p class="editorial-cta__back"><a href="/">返回主頁</a></p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .editorial-hero--short .editorial-hero__content {
    padding-top: 140px;
    padding-bottom: 96px;
  }

  .editorial-hero__image--spc {
    background-image:
      linear-gradient(rgba(32, 35, 31, 0.42), rgba(32, 35, 31, 0.62)),
      url('/images/projects/project-residential-01.jpg');
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }

  .editorial-material {
    padding: clamp(64px, 9vw, 120px) 0;
  }

  .editorial-material--alt {
    background: var(--mist, #f4f2ec);
  }

  .editorial-material__title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 40px);
    line-height: 1.18;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
    margin: 14px 0 clamp(36px, 5vw, 56px);
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .editorial-material__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(28px, 4vw, 56px);
  }

  .editorial-material__item {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding-top: 20px;
  }

  .editorial-material__index {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    color: var(--moss, #6c7355);
  }

  .editorial-material__item h3 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 20px;
    margin: 10px 0 10px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .editorial-material__item p {
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--ink-soft, #5c5f57);
  }

  .editorial-faq {
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
  }

  .editorial-faq__item {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding: 22px 0;
  }

  .editorial-faq__item summary {
    cursor: pointer;
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-size: 18px;
    color: var(--ink);
    list-style: none;
  }

  .editorial-faq__item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .editorial-faq__item summary::after {
    content: '+';
    float: right;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    color: var(--ink-soft, #5c5f57);
  }

  .editorial-faq__item[open] summary::after {
    content: '–';
  }

  .editorial-faq__item p {
    margin: 14px 0 0;
    font-size: 15px;
    line-height: 1.75;
    color: var(--ink-soft, #5c5f57);
    max-width: 60ch;
  }

  .editorial-faq__item a {
    color: var(--moss, #6c7355);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  .editorial-steps {
    list-style: none;
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: clamp(24px, 4vw, 48px);
  }

  .editorial-steps li {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    align-items: baseline;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--line);
    padding-top: 18px;
  }

  .editorial-steps li > span {
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--moss, #6c7355);
  }

  .editorial-steps h3 {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 19px;
    margin: 0 0 6px;
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .editorial-steps p {
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.65;
    color: var(--ink-soft, #5c5f57);
    margin: 0;
  }

  .editorial-cta {
    padding: clamp(72px, 10vw, 128px) 0;
    background: var(--ink);
    color: var(--paper);
  }

  .editorial-cta__title {
    font-family: var(--serif);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: clamp(26px, 4vw, 40px);
    line-height: 1.2;
    margin: 14px 0 16px;
  }

  .editorial-cta__body {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    max-width: 52ch;
    color: rgba(244, 242, 236, 0.78);
  }

  .editorial-cta__actions {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 16px;
    margin-top: 32px;
  }

  .editorial-cta__primary,
  .editorial-cta__ghost {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 14px 26px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: opacity 0.2s var(--ease);
  }

  .editorial-cta__primary {
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
  }

  .editorial-cta__ghost {
    border: 1px solid rgba(244, 242, 236, 0.4);
    color: var(--paper);
  }

  .editorial-cta__primary:hover,
  .editorial-cta__ghost:hover {
    opacity: 0.82;
  }

  .editorial-cta__back {
    margin-top: 28px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.06em;
  }

  .editorial-cta__back a {
    color: rgba(244, 242, 236, 0.7);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 3px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 720px) {
    .editorial-material__grid,
    .editorial-steps {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
